# 🍔 DB's Burgers - New York's Favorite Burger

A vibrant, fully animated landing page for DB's Burgers, a fictional burger restaurant with a bold personality and plant-based options.

![DB's Burgers Preview](https://i.imgur.com/aMLtAbd.png)

## 📋 Project Overview

DB's Burgers is a responsive, interactive landing page built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It features smooth animations, a mobile-friendly hamburger menu, and engaging scroll-based effects that showcase the brand's playful identity.

### 🌟 Key Features

- **Responsive Design** - Optimized for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
- **Interactive Hamburger Menu** - Smooth mobile navigation with animated transitions
- **Scroll-Based Animations** - Banner marquee effects that respond to scroll position
- **Hover Animations** - Burger cards with 3D sway effects and image lift
- **Custom Typography** - Oswald and Bowlby One fonts for bold, distinctive branding
- **Smooth Section Navigation** - Click-to-scroll functionality for all menu items
- **Dynamic Content** - JavaScript-generated repeating banner text

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

| Technology | Purpose |
|------------|---------|
| HTML5 | Semantic structure and content |
| CSS3 | Styling, animations, and responsive layouts |
| JavaScript (ES6+) | Interactivity and dynamic behavior |
| Google Fonts | Oswald & Bowlby One typefaces |
| SVG Icons | Scalable menu and rating icons |

